Class PodcastItemDataImpl

java.lang.Object
com.apptasticsoftware.rssreader.module.podcast.PodcastItemDataImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
PodcastItemData
public class PodcastItemDataImpl extends Object implements PodcastItemData
Implementation of PodcastItemData for managing podcast item metadata. Stores and provides access to podcast-specific information such as episodes, chapters, images, transcripts, and live item data.
